            "content": "http:\n  routers:\n    nas:\n      rule: Host(`nas.jclee.me`)\n      entryPoints:\n        - websecure\n      service: nas\n      tls:\n        certResolver: cf\n      priority: 10\n\n  services:\n    nas:\n      loadBalancer:\n        serversTransport: nas-transport\n        servers:\n          - url: https://192.168.50.215:5001\n\n  serversTransports:\n    nas-transport:\n      insecureSkipVerify: true\n",
